Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 啊 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静一点说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦？ 现在你们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 我又让你哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不可以的 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过要保护我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦... 鸦他...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开他 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为在这家伙的身边才会遇到这么危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦是想要保护我... 所以才变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 佑就是鸦 所以你会帮我的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥...
