Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭的粒子也完全消失掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是观测者们的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说鸦他...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了枭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么样的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着女人的幻影 连朋友都可以杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去 要不了多久\N拉库利玛就抑制不了香格里拉的侵蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把那家伙带到这片土地上来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要进行擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能够穿越时空的只剩下我们两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...不是为了让我吓一跳而准备的恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么来说明才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...这个家伙不是坏家伙就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想救他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么办 就算你这么问...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么直接去那孩子家里 不会被防备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使担心那样的事 也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽快和黛博士取得联络
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤一个人没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 雪惠也跟过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原君 抄近路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在做什...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉 你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉 哥哥一直在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态 变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗莉控啊 罗莉控!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得那家伙很危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人好奇怪啊 我可不是什么莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像把你误认成了自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会危害到你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不像坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原君原来是个胆小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我看你们很慌张的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为...为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这些家伙也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...自然而然就成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说过了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 后藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙也不是那么厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像失去记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 睡着了可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哭呢 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你听得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很严重啊 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在严重衰弱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做点什么吧 你们不都是一样是未来人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未...未来人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我再生会消耗太多的粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭在哪里 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是燕雀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你拥有可以看见时空的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:10:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后根据你所看到的 来确定时空 来变成你的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戴着假面的人 不是那个人 也不是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦不会死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 粒子会完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦也会消失...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 做些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找到可以大量补充粒子的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能做些什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子是构成所有物质的最初的单位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的物质 所有的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掌握时间和空间根源性的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这个时代还没有被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得懂吗 雪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空里也应该有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的终极点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果朝这个点前进的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果去那里的话 鸦就可以得救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要将那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张脸...是说收获为零咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一个收获
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛拓野不在那个屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的鞋子连一双都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗 不窄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯这样的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那请忍耐一下吧 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 你说你不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...车子里坐不下所有人不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使我去了也帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你就和上乃木一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一旦发生了什么立刻联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 要振作一点 拿出点精神来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到刚才的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...我们正朝哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前有量子计划的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那个老师飙起车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 给我好好抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老...老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大姐往哪里开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说话 会咬到舌头的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大姐真的什么都做的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 他们不是要走了吗 那个随便乱说的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌慌张张也无济于事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有跟上来了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了 粒子集中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 都聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能杀死枭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是鸦 也不是那么简单可以干掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死枭的不是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会相信叛徒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭 够了住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要向我求饶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...你们的命怎么也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龙之转矩交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空和拉库利玛一样还没有达到临界点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正是因为是在这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩才可能成为保持全时空稳定的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想听你的什么预测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要把龙之转矩带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我们龙骑兵唯一的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连你也会顾同伴情谊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 把生命之光...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不要问了 老师 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个人要比表面看起来的要轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会让你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...真的是燕雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云都流过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连战斗的方法都忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明跟我说了那么多了不起的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把遥弄哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你不是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是 你也是 龙骑兵也完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体正在恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢君 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我看到了那样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不能被选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什么人所决定的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对不会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我和那个人一起走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦也能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么总是能让我焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉库利玛成为幻影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 这么多粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到遥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还停留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空的遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不允许擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来是无限延伸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定我们也能够选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.81,0:24:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
